Package Server

Interface ServerCallbacks

All Known Implementing Classes:
ChooseSongViewController, FriendViewController, LogInUserController, RegisterUserController
public interface ServerCallbacks
this interface is used as an observer to notify whoever implements it about the information received by the server

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void onSongReceived​(Song song)
    this method is called when the server receives a requested song
    void onUserReceived()
    this method is called when a user is received by the server
    void onUserSongsReceived​(java.util.ArrayList<BasicInfoSong> songs)
    this method is called when the user's songs are received
